name: Cachet Financial Solutions
overview: achet Financial Solutions, Inc. provides hosted remote deposit capture (RDC) solutions for banks, credit unions, and other financial institutions. It offers RDC Select, an integrated platform that enables financial institutions to deliver RDC services to their customers. The company’s commercial and consumer RDC products include Select Business, a merchant capture solution for PC and Mac users; Select Home, a consumer capture for small/home offices; and Select Mobile, a mobile remote deposit capture solution. In addition, it offers Mobile Check Capture, a mobile check capture solution for financial service organizations/prepaid cards; CheckReview, a real time image verification solution for RDC; Select Capture, a branch capture solution; and Select Remittance, a remittance processing solution. Further, the company provides product training, implementation, marketing, security and compliance, and technical support services. Cachet Financial Solutions, Inc. was incorporated in 2010 and is based in Minneapolis, Minnesota.
